empty?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216280/extras/d8fead2cb31272105ed317df8fd2e3ff.avif?t=1770668826\" width=1560 height=86 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration &amp; Puzzles</strong><br>Search classrooms, offices, and ruined corridors for clues. The building itself resists you - collapsing elements, locked doors, and fragments of a story hidden in forgotten corners.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Non-Linear Storytelling</strong><br>Multiple paths, multiple endings. Environmental storytelling leads you forward, but the truth won’t be handed to you. Optional secrets reveal answers you weren’t even asking for.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hunted in the Dark</strong><br>You’re not alone. Keep your flashlight close - the shadows are watching, and they move when you don’t.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216280/extras/73ca2dcb98acb4426b133a1249fe9d48.avif?t=1770668826\" width=1560 height=86 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No saves - immersion is survival</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Headphones recommended for full impact</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This psychological horror game deals with heavy themes which may be upsetting. Play at your own discretion.</strong></p>",
